  "title": "Short Weaponry",
  "description": "A PvP pack that turns weapons into shorter variants: short- sword, axe, bow and mini mace",
  "body": "![Short Weaponry](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f3c2afb5fb6b0aaab5ddcf29e991050adf0e4d12.png)\n\n## Welcome to Short Weaponry\nA resource pack made to expand on the idea of a short sword pack.\n\n### This resource pack features:\n- Short Swords ![Neth sword](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/12bcc703b97a87e143c6366d1f57dd3bbf3ec876.png)\n- Short Axes ![Neth axe](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7d80cc26913746fbef9516be67b3852fae688ab0.png)\n- Short Bow ![Bow](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/584bc79c11ea9eb4c481a995e9ba24e9cb772c1b.png)\n- Mini Mace ![Mace](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ffe3f94f8c8ba54d04761aff48fc90b526d69c07.png)\n\nCredit for the short sword texture: VanillaTweaks\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pnPewT4xpE\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/347e3d1419da95e567713c06878aa2dab4b14c30.png\" alt=\"Join the Discord server\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n\n## Other projects:\n\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/armored-vanguard\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c9ed2b7145c975776d07353bd57247825ad1b852_0.webp\" alt=\"Armored Vanguard\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/armored-vanguard-dyed-knights\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/86ed16bfaa663826eb949e88736a5bf32daf1532_0.webp\" alt=\"Armored Vanguard: Dyed Knights\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/spears-to-lances\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e223d249862cd3bf02859137f046ca13427af596.png\" alt=\"Spears to Lances\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/craftmas-chests\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/509bb6a689a5f8a42ae66d8901710552cb5d5ba7_0.webp\" alt=\"Christmas Containers\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/nomex-helmets\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8316fb689873e46e8bb67397d82f295730ee6afc.png\" alt=\"Racing Helmets\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>",
